        "en": "Mutation or genetic engineering; DNA or RNA concerning genetic engineering, vectors, e.g. plasmids, or their isolation, preparation or purification; Use of hosts therefor (mutants or genetically engineered microorganisms C12N0001000000, C12N0005000000, C12N0007000000;new plants A01H;plant reproduction by tissue culture techniques A01H0004000000;new animals A01K0067000000;use of medicinal preparations containing genetic material which is inserted into cells of the living body to treat genetic diseases, gene therapy A61K0048000000;peptides in general C07K)"
